om-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; ba=
ckground-color: #ccc;">  keep quoting it</a> because it is such cinematic f=
oreshadowing, but last year Bankman-Fried <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/30059877.263533/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9=
